snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Oracle of Secrets Trailer
snippet.description:
The Legend of Zelda: Oracle of Secrets is a Link to the Past ROM hack which completely reimagines the game with a new world, story, items, bosses, and more! In development for well over a decade, the game is nearing completion and looking for beta testers to help finish out development for a release sometime this summer.

Frozen Hyrule theme interpolated @letterbomb5065 

https://discord.gg/MBFkMTPEmk
